Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:09.01,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}I had lost my way during my journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:17.02,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Only my soul was wandering, while I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:25.28,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}But right now, I'm walking to a distant place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:33.53,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}That's right, ever since I met you on this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:41.96,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}The travellers witnessed the song, the forbidden song,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:52.72,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}And I became attached to it as I heard it alone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:01:00.81,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}If the world I saw in my dreams exists somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:09.20,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Let's go search for it, beyond the winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:13.37,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Whether it's a freezing dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:17.58,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A dry midday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.75,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A shivering night,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:28.00,op_style,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}or the ends of the Earth, let's go and see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:48.43,Chapter Name Title Style,,0000,0000,0000,,Wolf and New Journey
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:06.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that we'd have a touching reunion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,but you look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This was all I could protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:16.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:18.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is swollen from being hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you're covered with mud, and even your wrist is burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And even with your foolish state,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:30.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,you protected my clothes with such devotion so they wouldn't become wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:33.65,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an unbelievable softy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.44,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.44,0:02:45.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to hasten our plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:48.28,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you and I could return to traveling without cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:51.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't fight with those arrogant youngsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and settled it by mature means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:57.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... right before them, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, it was something that I decided on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.37,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is my repayment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,With your pathetic state,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go immediately to that Remerio man's place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,and make him pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on, first we have to deal with Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And as fast as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a satisfying reason, then tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're planning to kill Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:36.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She has her partner, I'm sure she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,She does, but there's a limit to how reckless they can be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it were me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:46.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were you, you could take care of a hundred armed men with ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd be a wolf during that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And that girl is a shepherd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, could you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:07.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just abandon them, knowing that they'll be killed unjustly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.36,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'll pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:12.35,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:16.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can save Nora's life, I will pay you back to the best of your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:20.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.15,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking off my clothes would be better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome to prepare new ones for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.73,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Under one condition, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who it may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:44.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot guarantee their lives if they test my temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you acknowledge that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.45,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:52.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become a smooth talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What a troublesome traveling companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.05,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:10.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a magnificent tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That was somewhat monotonous, but very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, could you close your eyes for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fall, you'll be riding in my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let go even if I die-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:46.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually really hate shepherds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that relieves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:06:00.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether this job fails or succeeds, Nora will stop being a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided on what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:05.92,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The best honey peaches there are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gentle the-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Lawrence and Horo have?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:17.23,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time we found them, we could barely tell it was them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The two were piled together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:22.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:26.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:29.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's really unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:34.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We survivors should continue and do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:37.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:40.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught up to them already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anyone, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:48.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,They're quite well armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are about twenty of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:51.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That many?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I jump over them, I'll back away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When I do, you jump off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the shepherd and sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the shepherd and run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Shepherd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:07:59.95,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:10.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you three hundred Rumione if you protect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:21.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:08:59.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Nora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:18.61,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.74,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not... a ghost, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you in on the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:40.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That wolf is Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:47.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:52.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I did think of swallowing him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:54.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that my stomach likes gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:58.24,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards! Don't think you'll get away after doing-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day, Mr. Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the one who betrayed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe me! I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:23.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,This wolf is an agent of the almighty God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:26.27,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Lying won't do you any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:32.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The payment you guys demanded was too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:36.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we had gone with the original plan, we'd pay off our debt, but there wouldn't be any profit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:39.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Remerio told me to do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.25,0:10:42.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are merch-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:54.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In brief, Remerio has betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they were planning to kill you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a vague idea they would, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:07.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, should we take the gold and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:10.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:17.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without smuggling, the gold Liebert bought amounts to 400 Rumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:23.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ignore the Remerio Company who betrayed us, we can live well-off for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:26.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if it weren't for the Remerio Company's investments,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:28.33,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't have obtained this gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:35.01,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we take away this gold, they will no doubt go bankrupt and be thrown into the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:35.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.00,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to live after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:52.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get revenge because we were betrayed, more vengeance will be waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:57.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that you'll bite everyone to death who was involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:12:01.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Using money stained with a person's blood to buy bread is a terrible feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:05.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many ways to settle things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:08.83,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to make the choice that'll lead us to tomorrow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:15.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo, if you weren't there, I would probably be freezing to death now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.77,0:12:18.71,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also very thankful that you listened to my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:22.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, do whatever pleases you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:26.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, my companion is so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.13,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:34.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I mentioned, this is my proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:40.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:44.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell me how it really is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:49.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb, you're not that virtuous of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:55.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Please decide whether we take this gold into Rubinheigen or not, Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:59.53,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind splitting half of what we took.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:00.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:05.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}However, if we bring it and rely on some connections, we can make ten times the amount, or six thousand Rumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.59,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Six thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:11.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that much, we can also save the Remerio Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped if you saw through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't enough gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:22.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be impossible to get six hundred Rumione with that amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Only about one hundred at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:28.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,After splitting half the share, you'd only be able to pay off your debt, and that'd be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:31.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means we won't see any profits unless we smuggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:33.96,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, they were under the pressure of necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:39.63,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35}They were only able to obtain a tenth of what they planned, one hundred Rumione, from scrounging up what they could.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:45.46,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}They'd smuggle the gold they bought and thought it would be okay if they could get one thousand Rumione.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:51.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So they knew they didn't have enough to pay us to keep quiet from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:56.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably why they agreed to the proposal we brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:00.43,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I understand their situation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:02.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:06.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need to say it to the little girl like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:08.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I put on too much of an act?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.54,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something you need to burden yourself with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.86,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more that I want to say, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to go to Remerio, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Business dealings have nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't pay attention, you'll fly off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.41,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Five hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:53.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:57.42,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In the event that we succeed in smuggling,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:15:01.08,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,will you buy the gold at five hundred Rumione?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.72,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:05.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we could do that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you won't have to pay it in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:13.90,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to write a promissory note and return it to us in small payments over ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.30,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But five hundred is just too-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:21.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have made many fine acquaintances in this town with loading spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.94,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred Rumione over ten years will be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:28.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about this from Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than taking flight in the night with these little assets,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:42.12,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,accepting our demands and rebuilding your store is more advantageous, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:46.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Send your debts to the Rowen Trading Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:53.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You may betray me, but if you betray the Trading Guild, that'll be the end of your days as a merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:57.22,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wouldn't be able to see you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:15:59.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you for scaring me, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.10,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:06.81,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're such an eccentric son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:18.75,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can cut your ties with Remerio and turn their debt into money after ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.34,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I just traded some gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:25.47,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really say it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll buy thirty for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:32.39,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If your dealings succeed, I'll buy another hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy, so it's a big bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.78,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:43.31,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have that much, I might just joke around, say my apologies, and then pay off my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:48.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become a great merchant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.38,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, once we're done with the audit, we're going to drink until we drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:54.52,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.63,0:16:56.55,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,My companion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:58.66,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you want to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:05.20,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:05.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much do you trust that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:14.14,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If she runs away with the gold now, we can still chase her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:19.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Anticipating that, I don't trust Nora enough to hand her the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.64,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought it'd be something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the other question?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll answer whatever you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you a lot this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.56,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:52.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you... remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:58.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was confronting the dog and the girl, whose name did you call?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:03.06,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood got to my head, so I couldn't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.62,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure you called one of our names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:11.25,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:12.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.40,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't worry me that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.89,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I called your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.11,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.76,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.49,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:03.16,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:08.32,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,In that situation, I'm sure I called your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.67,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,A conflict was about to begin, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:14.85,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I unconsciously chose to call your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:15.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.21,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.80,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can say it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:28.60,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is a bit shorter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:47.48,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,With Nora, you'd be able to tell right away if you said her name fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:51.18,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,But with Horo, you can say it in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.87,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood was going to your head, so you probably didn't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.88,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? I'm just overflowing with persuasi-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.09,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.91,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You called my name just because it's a bit shorter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:02.29,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:07.02,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm angry because you actually think that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:10.51,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had said that you called out that girl's name...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.98,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've scratched you with all I had!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.57,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.58,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Try saying my name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:29.82,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:32.97,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is better, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:35.93,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.84,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:47.03,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to clear the false accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:50.70,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:53.79,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He just realized my true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.99,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:59.04,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:02.19,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,He's more useful than this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:03.07,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.68,SpicyWolf,,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy, you two.
